<para
>In these modules, you can configure various aspects of &konqueror;'s file manager functionality. </para>

<note
><para
>&konqueror;'s web browser functionality has its <ulink url="help:/kcontrol/khtml-behavior/index.html"
>own configuration modules</ulink
>.</para
></note>

