<varlistentry>
<term
><guilabel
>Відкривати теки у окремих вікнах</guilabel
></term>
<listitem
> <para
>If this option is checked, a new &konqueror; window will be created when you open a folder, rather than simply showing that folder's contents in the current window.</para
></listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term
><guilabel
>Show 'Delete' menu entries which bypass the trashcan</guilabel
></term>
<listitem>
<para
>Check this if you want <quote
>Delete</quote
> menu commands to be displayed on the desktop and in the file manager's context menus. You can always delete files by holding the &Shift; key while calling <guimenuitem
>Move to Trash</guimenuitem
>.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>
</variablelist>

